# Secure API Middleware Project
This project includes a secure API backend with Express and a React frontend.

**Student Name**: Rithik Subasinghe
**Student ID**: 20210166/ w1870601
**Module**: 6COSC022W – Web Design & Development  
**Coursework 1** – Secure API Country details Fetch System  
**Last Updated**: 10th April 2025


# Tech Stack

Frontend: React.js (with React Router)

Backend: Node.js + Express.js

Database: SQLite (for users & API keys)

Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Token)

API Integration: https://restcountries.com

# How to Run

1. Clone the Repository

git clone 
cd country-details-app

2. Start Backend

cd backend
npm install
node server.js

3. Start Frontend

cd ../frontend
npm install
npm start


## Run
node server3.js

## Run Docker
docker run -p 3000:3000 cw

